{"lemma":"عُرْضَةٍ","slug":"عُرْضَةٍ","root":"ع.ر.ض","root_slug":"ع-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عُرْضَة","root":"عرض","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28682","n28693"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28682","headword_ar":"عرّضهُ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriyDN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AErDhu","text_ar":"اعرضهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEoraADN","text_ar":"اـِعْرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  See also 1, near the end, in three places. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEariyDN","text_ar":"تَعَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The speaking obliquely, indirectly, obscurely, ambiguously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equivocally; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSoriyHN","text_ar":"تَصْرِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as when thou askest a man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hast thou seen such a one?"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and he, having seen him, and disliking to lie, answers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily such a one is seen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"” (Msb:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making a phrase,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, to convey an allusion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an indication not expressly mentioned therein; as when you say"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How foul is niggardliness!"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"alluding to such a one's being a niggard"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuEar~iDu biA^an~ahu","text_ar":"تُعَرِّضُ بِاَنَّهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baxiylN","text_ar":"بَخِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kinaAyapN","text_ar":"كِنَايَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the mentioning of the consequence and meaning that of which it is the consequence; as when you say “ Such a one has a long suspensory cord to his sword, and has many ashes of the cooking-pot; ” meaning that he is tall of stature, and one who entertains many guests: (Mgh:) [but many hold these two words to be identical in meaning.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ear~aDotu lifulaAnK","text_ar":"عَرَّضْتُ لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bifulaAnK","text_ar":"بِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I said something"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the manner explained above"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meaning such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb.) [See also an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kal~aA='N","text_ar":"كَلَّا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] 'Omar defined [or rather explained]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aEoriyDu biAlfaAHi$api","text_ar":"التَّعْرِيضُ بِالفَاحِشَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The making an allusion to that which is foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by the instance of a man saying to another “ My father is not an adulterer, nor is my mother an adulteress. ” (O, TA.) Or, accord. to the early authorities,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~D","text_ar":"عرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He used a phrase susceptible of different meanings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an equivocal phrase, by which the hearer understood a meaning different from that which he"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the speaker"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intended:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to the later authorities, as Et-Teftezánee,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he mentioned a thing by a proper or tropical or metonymical expression, to signify some other thing, which he did not mention;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as when one says, “ I heard him whom thou hatest praying for thee, and making good mention of thee; ” meaning in his praying for the Muslims in general. (El-Munáwee, in explaining the trad."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a fiY AlmaEaAriyDi Alx","text_ar":"اـِنَّ فِى المَعَارِيضِ الخ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see below, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEoraADN","text_ar":"مِعْرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEryD","text_ar":"تعريض"},{"kind":"text","text":"with respect to the demanding of a woman in marriage in [the period of] her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eid~ap","text_ar":"عِدَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", [during which she may not contract a new marriage,] is the using language which resembles a demand of her in marriage, but does not plainly express it; as the saying to her “ Verily thou art beautiful, ” or “ Verily there is a desire for thee, ” or “ Verily women are of the things that I need: ” and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEryD","text_ar":"تعريض"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes made by the quoting of proverbs, and by the introducing of enigmas in one's speech. (TA.) [When followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY","text_ar":"عَلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", it signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making an indirect objection"},{"kind":"text","text":"against a person or saying &c.] ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~D","text_ar":"عرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) inf. n. as above, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote indistinctly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not making the letters distinct, nor the handwriting rightly formed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriyDN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also sigsifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be exposed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liable"},{"kind":"text","text":"] to another thing. (K, [It is there expl., with the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to it, by the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano yajoEala","text_ar":"اَنْ يَجْعَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lil$~aYo'i","text_ar":"لِلشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'a EaroDFA","text_ar":"الشَّىْءَ عَرْضًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraDFA","text_ar":"عَرَضًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different copies; the latter (which see, last sentence but one,) app. the right reading; meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoruwDFA","text_ar":"مَعْرُوضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", whichever be the right; for an inf. n. may be used in the sense of a pass. part. n.; and many a word of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalN","text_ar":"فَعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used in that sense, as, for instance,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabaTN","text_ar":"خَبَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafaDN","text_ar":"نَفَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hadamN","text_ar":"هَدَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". That I have rightly rendered the above-mentioned explanation in the K is indicated by what here immediately follows.]) Hence the trad."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EaZumato","text_ar":"مَا عَظُمَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niEomapu A@ll~`hi EalaY EabodK A_il~aA EaZumato maw^uwnapu Aln~aAsi Ealayohi","text_ar":"نِعْمَةُ ا@للّٰهِ عَلَى عَبْدٍ اـِلَّا عَظُمَتْ مَوُونَةُ النَّاسِ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"famano lamo yaHotamilo tiloka Almaw^uwnapa faqado Ear~aDa tiloka Aln~iEomapa","text_ar":"فَمَنْ لَمْ يَحْتَمِلْ تِلْكَ المَوُونَةَ فَقَدْ عَرَّضَ تِلْكَ النِّعْمَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilz~awaAli","text_ar":"لِلزَّوَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The blessing of God upon a servant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"man, hath not become great but the burden of"},{"kind":"text","text":"other"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"men upon him hath become great; and he who doth not take upon himself that burden causeth that blessing to be exposed to cessation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) You also say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa lahu","text_ar":"هُوَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ear~aDotu fulaAnFA lika*aA fataEar~aDa","text_ar":"عَرَّضْتُ فُلَانًا لِكَذَا فَتَعَرَّضَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I caused such a one to expose himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I exposed him, to such a thing, and he exposed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became exposed, to it"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, O, *) i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalotuhu EaraDFA","text_ar":"جَعَلْتُهُ عَرَضًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lika*aA","text_ar":"لِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) See also 1, last quarter. ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving a thing in exchange for, as an equivalent for,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the place of, another thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of bartering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"selling, a commodity for a like commodity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) See 3, in two places. ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving what is termed an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADap","text_ar":"عُرَاضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feeding with what is so termed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving food of what is so termed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) [See also 1, near the end.] It is said in a trad., respecting a company of travelling merchants making presents to Mohammad and Aboo-Bekr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ear~aDuwhumaA viyaAbFA biyDFA","text_ar":"عَرَّضُوهُمَا ثِيَابًا بِيضًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They gave to both of them white garments,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of cloth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ear~aDuwhumo maHoDFA","text_ar":"عَرَّضُوهُمْ مَحْضًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They gave them to drink"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unmixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ear~iDuwnaA","text_ar":"عَرِّضُونَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Give ye to us food of your"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADap","text_ar":"عُرَاضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"your wheat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corn, which ye have brought."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~D AlmaA$iyapa","text_ar":"عرّض المَاشِيَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriyDN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the cattle to have such pasturage as rendered them in no need of being fed with fodder."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~D","text_ar":"عرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriyDN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became possessed of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAriDap","text_ar":"عَارِضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"courage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"courage and energy"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (IAar, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and a faculty of speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K,) or, as in the Tekmileh,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and power of speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He kept continually to the eating of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiroDaAn","text_ar":"عِرْضَان"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, * K, TA, [in the O"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraAD","text_ar":"عِرَاض"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariyDN","text_ar":"عَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A5-  See also 4, last sentence."}],"source_refs":["Lth","S","K","Msb","Mgh","O","TA","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n28693","headword_ar":"عُرْضَةٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEolapN","text_ar":"فُعْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quboDapN","text_ar":"قُبْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Bd, ii. 224;) and is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is set as an obstacle in the way of a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, TA:) and also to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is exposed to a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is set as a butt, like the butt of archers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalotu fulaAnFA EuroDapF lika*aA","text_ar":"جَعَلْتُ فُلَانًا عُرْضَةً لِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSabotuhu","text_ar":"نَصَبْتُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K; *) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I set such a one as an obstacle to such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a butt for such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa lahu duwnahu EuroDapN","text_ar":"هُوَ لَهُ دُونَهُ عُرْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is an obstacle to him intervening in the way of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN EuroDapN liln~aAsi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ عُرْضَةٌ لِلنَّاسِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a butt to men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person whom men cease not to revile:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person to whom men address themselves to do evil, and whom they revile."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo DuEafaA='u EuroDapN likul~i mutanaAwilK","text_ar":"هُمْ ضُعَفَا=ءُ عُرْضَةٌ لِكُلِّ مُتَنَاوِلٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are weak persons; persons who offer themselves as a prey to any one who would take them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And it is said in the Kur [ii. 224],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA tajoEaluwA","text_ar":"وَلَا تَجْعَلُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu EuroDapF liA^ayomaAnikumo A^ano tabar~uwA watat~aquwA watuSoliHuwA bayona","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ عُرْضَةً لِاَيْمَانِكُمْ اَنْ تَبَرُّوا وَتَتَّقُوا وَتُصْلِحُوا بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * &c.,) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSobFA","text_ar":"نَصْبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) admitting the two significations of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an obstacle"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a butt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And make not God an obstacle"},{"kind":"text","text":"between you and that which may bring you near unto God, &c.: (O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make not God an obstacle to the performance of your oaths to be pious"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Bd)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and to fear God and to make reconciliation between men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make not God an obstacle, because of your oaths, to your being pious"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make not the swearing by God an obstacle to your being pious"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]: (Fr:) and Zj says the like of this: (L:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDapN","text_ar":"عُرْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervention"},{"kind":"text","text":"with respect to good and evil; (Abu-l- 'Abbás, O, K;) and the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"do not intervene by swearing by God every little while so as not to be pious"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (O, K, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make not God an object of your oaths, by ordinary and frequent swearing by Him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a butt for your oaths, like the butt of archers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that ye may be pious"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; for the habitual swearer emboldens himself against God, and is not pious &c.: (Bd:) or, as some say, the meaning is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make not the mention of God a means of strengthening your oaths."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA EuroDapN laka","text_ar":"هٰذَا عُرْضَةٌ لَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is a thing prepared for thy common,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordinary, use."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A purpose; an intention;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of endeavour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though it were a butt;] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"him~apN","text_ar":"هِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.) Hassán says, (S, O,) i. e. Ibn-Thábit, (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"waqaAla A@ll~`hu qado yas~arotu junodFA\n                      \n                     \n                        humu AlA^anoSaAru EuroDatuhaA All~iqaA='u"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And God said I have prepared an army: they are the Ansár; whose purpose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the object of whose desire, is conflict"},{"kind":"text","text":"with the unbelievers]. (S, O, TA. [In one copy of the S, in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yas~arotu","text_ar":"يَسَّرْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", I find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEodadotu","text_ar":"اَعْدَدْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies the same.]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pretext; an excuse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) ―         -b4-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN EuroDapu *aAka","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ عُرْضَةُ ذَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDapN li*aAka","text_ar":"عُرْضَةٌ لِذَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is possessed of the requisite ability and strength for that:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDapN lil$~ar~i","text_ar":"عُرْضَةٌ لِلشَّرِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessed of strength to do evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mischief:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDapN","text_ar":"عُرْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to two things, and to more. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnapu EuroDapN lilz~awoji","text_ar":"فُلَانَةُ عُرْضَةٌ لِلزَّوْجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a female is possessed of sufficient strength for the husband;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., to be married;] (TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liln~ikaAHi","text_ar":"لِلنِّكَاحِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for marriage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN EuroDapN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ عُرْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloHijaArapi","text_ar":"لِلْحِجَارَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel having strength enough for"},{"kind":"text","text":"[going upon]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the stones."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) And [in like manner]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaArK","text_ar":"اَسْفَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN EuroDu","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ عُرْضُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel having strength sufficient for journeys."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA AlbaEiyri Als~afaru waAlHajaru","text_ar":"هٰذَا البَعِيرِ السَّفَرُ وَالحَجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDu","text_ar":"عُرْضُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The strength of this camel is sufficient for journeying and for going over stone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDapN","text_ar":"عُرْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of trick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"artifice, in wrestling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,) by which one throws down men. (S, O.)"}],"source_refs":["Bd","TA","S","O","Msb","K","Fr","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}